                    <description>Couchbase Lite API references.</description>
                    <introduction>
                        <paragraph>Couchbase Lite is an embedded NoSQL database that can work standalone, in a P2P network, or as a remote endpoint for Couchbase Server. This section provides API references guides for both Couchbase Lite native platform support, as well as REST support.
